{"tid":1336132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"從銀髮族手中收到份好珍貴好感動嘅禮物...","createTime":"2019-07-20T20:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T05:55:14.000Z","uid":24050,"like":105,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f25e17a9654cdc7b6f410fa2bebea2946e76a5ee","tid":1336132,"uid":24050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T20:00:32.000Z","msg":"話說星期三銀髮族遊行，我陪咗家母出去行<br />\n我哋前面有兩個叔叔<br />\n舉緊自己用毛筆寫嘅紙banner<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我見佢哋行到身水身汗，<br />\n就喺後面幫佢地撥涼加傾咗幾句偈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知行行吓突然有陣怪風，吹爛左張banner<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n叔叔之後送咗張banner畀我留念<br />\n話未來交畀我哋年青人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我應承佢，修補好之後7.21會帶埋佢出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vuofETA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvuofETA.png&h=cde83a4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多謝你叔叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝所有銀髮族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n7.21，有唔少銀髮族都會再出嚟遊行，<br />\n有啲甚至話想上前線位置，<br />\n作為同警察溝通嘅橋樑，保護年青人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n年青人，係時候行出嚟答謝銀髮族嘅支持、<br />\n保護返佢哋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然，最重要嘅係 真。守護香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人，晏啲見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"8b18ec9413cd7c2d125b76aedbf398d2f1ddb0ef","tid":1336132,"uid":143151,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T20:03:15.000Z","msg":"真係想講<br />\n銀髮族手字靚過我哋個啲好多<br />\n究竟係咩因素影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939d4d62f3c6fe700492258bff1e0db8eadd756e","tid":1336132,"uid":269119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T20:06:23.000Z","msg":"第三個字寫甚麼？<br />\n還我？港"},{"pid":"86cfe7bb0ba0d8f7d05a8afd517d0d88480fad0f","tid":1336132,"uid":265305,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"8b18ec9413cd7c2d125b76aedbf398d2f1ddb0ef","tid":1336132,"uid":143151,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T20:03:15.000Z","msg":"真係想講<br />\n銀髮族手字靚過我哋個啲好多<br />\n究竟係咩因素影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T20:06:52.000Z","msg":"通識係公廁罪因走唔甩咖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得係用電腦手機多，大家都打字多過寫字<br />\n有口字既字我係中6貪快由右至左後到而加都改唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81cb3f5158c0faf4d807f19c552a292c50bc9c46","tid":1336132,"uid":173058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T20:26:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全純黑色好重要，圓領T-shirt包頭最有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打機前記得攞黑色膠紙包起對鞋啊！！<br />\n警犬認鞋架！<br />\n旺角篤魚蛋有幾個被人判刑都係因為衣物！</span></span>"},{"pid":"8ddbb9f338c0386a373456621461b8fcbb591724","tid":1336132,"uid":27